        <h1>WSO2 Governance Registry - Issue Tracking</h1>
        <strong>Issue Tracking for WSO2 Governance Registry</strong>
        <p>Issues, bugs, improvements and feature requests for the <a class="externalLink" href="http://www.wso2.com/products/governance-registry">
            WSO2 Governance Registry</a> should be submitted to the following issue tracking system.</p>
        <div class="source">
            <a class="externalLink" href="http://wso2.org/jira/browse/REGISTRY">http://wso2.org/jira/browse/REGISTRY</a>
        </div>
        <strong>Issue Tracking for WSO2 Carbon Platform</strong>
        <p>
            WSO2 Governance Registry is developed on top of the <a class="externalLink" href="http://www.wso2.com/products/carbon">
            WSO2 Carbon platform</a>. To get an overall
            idea on the issue management of the WSO2 Governance Registry, you might need to have a look at the
            WSO2 Carbon platform's issue tracking as well.
        </p>
        <p>
            Issues, bugs, improvements and feature requests for the WSO2 Carbon platform should be submitted to the following issue tracking system.</p>
        <div class="source">
            <a class="externalLink" href="http://wso2.org/jira/browse/CARBON">http://wso2.org/jira/browse/CARBON</a>
        </div>
        <p> If you are simply interested in the Governance and Registry component specific issues, have a look at </p>
        <div class="source">
            <a class="externalLink" href="https://wso2.org/jira/browse/CARBON/component/10391">Registry components' core issues</a>
            <br/>
            <a class="externalLink" href="https://wso2.org/jira/browse/CARBON/component/10402">Registry components' UI issues</a>
            <br/>
            <a class="externalLink" href="https://wso2.org/jira/browse/CARBON/component/10475">Governance components' core issues</a>
            <br/>
            <a class="externalLink" href="https://wso2.org/jira/browse/CARBON/component/10476">Governance components' UI issues</a>
            <br/>
            <a class="externalLink" href="https://wso2.org/jira/browse/CARBON/component/10502">Registry Remote API issues</a>
            <br/>
            <a class="externalLink" href="https://wso2.org/jira/browse/CARBON/component/10404">Registry documentation issues</a>
            <br/>
        </div>

        <h2 id="jira">Issue Tracking System</h2>
        <p>
            This project uses
            <a class="externalLink" href="http://www.atlassian.com/software/jira">Atlassian JIRA</a>, a J2EE-based,
            issue tracking and project management application. You can find more information on how to report an issue
            form
            <a class="externalLink" href="http://www.atlassian.com/software/jira/docs/v3.13/introduction.html">
                Atlassian JIRA help pages.</a>
        </p>

